{"words":[{"word":"ogo","count":4},{"word":"into","count":4},{"word":"tacet","count":4},{"word":"take","count":4},{"word":"fractsidus","count":2},{"word":"stronger","count":2},{"word":"less","count":2},{"word":"discords","count":2},{"word":"course","count":2},{"word":"move","count":2},{"word":"frequencies","count":2},{"word":"discord","count":2},{"word":"new","count":2},{"word":"friend","count":2},{"word":"time","count":2},{"word":"stay","count":2},{"word":"hey","count":1},{"word":"showtime","count":1},{"word":"else","count":1},{"word":"live","count":1},{"word":"power","count":1},{"word":"exactly","count":1},{"word":"turn","count":1},{"word":"weak","count":1},{"word":"mighty","count":1},{"word":"nobodies","count":1},{"word":"somebodies","count":1},{"word":"mere","count":1},{"word":"mortals","count":1},{"word":"gods","count":1},{"word":"relax","count":1},{"word":"another","count":1},{"word":"tweak","count":1},{"word":"upgrade","count":1},{"word":"makes","count":1},{"word":"constrained","count":1},{"word":"beast","count":1},{"word":"gorgeous","count":1},{"word":"strong","count":1},{"word":"sharp","count":1},{"word":"claws","count":1},{"word":"glossy","count":1},{"word":"fur","count":1},{"word":"bulging","count":1},{"word":"muscles","count":1},{"word":"listen","count":1},{"word":"curses","count":1},{"word":"miracles","count":1},{"word":"honor","count":1},{"word":"harnessing","count":1},{"word":"miracle","count":1},{"word":"pouring","count":1},{"word":"money","count":1},{"word":"kicks","count":1},{"word":"fire","count":1},{"word":"machine","count":1},{"word":"transformed","count":1},{"word":"able","count":1},{"word":"touch","count":1},{"word":"i'll","count":1},{"word":"upstairs","count":1},{"word":"ladder","count":1},{"word":"goodbye","count":1},{"word":"grunt","count":1},{"word":"work","count":1},{"word":"hahaha","count":1},{"word":"genius","count":1},{"word":"using","count":1},{"word":"human","count":1},{"word":"long","count":1},{"word":"understand","count":1},{"word":"language","count":1},{"word":"boss","count":1},{"word":"around","count":1},{"word":"however","count":1},{"word":"shut","count":1},{"word":"photonvault","count":1},{"word":"release","count":1},{"word":"mean","count":1},{"word":"old","count":1},{"word":"rover","count":1},{"word":"stand","count":1},{"word":"chance","count":1},{"word":"hear","count":1},{"word":"body","count":1},{"word":"feeling","count":1},{"word":"four","count":1},{"word":"legs","count":1},{"word":"challenge","count":1},{"word":"first","count":1},{"word":"stupid","count":1},{"word":"combined","count":1},{"word":"moron","count":1},{"word":"funny","count":1},{"word":"wake","count":1},{"word":"nap","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Hey, Ogo, it’s showtime!","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016},{"text":"Who else? You want to live, right? You want power, don’t you? That’s exactly what the Fractsidus is all about.","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016},{"text":"We turn the weak into the mighty, the nobodies into somebodies, and mere mortals into… gods.","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016},{"text":"Relax, it’s just another tweak. Like the upgrade you had before—only this makes you stronger and less constrained.","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016},{"text":"Look at this beast—gorgeous, isn’t it? Strong, too. Those sharp claws, that glossy fur, those bulging muscles…","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016},{"text":"Listen, Tacet Discords are not curses, they’re miracles. And now, you get the honor of harnessing that miracle. Don’t let me down.","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016},{"text":"Of course, Ogo. The Fractsidus isn’t pouring money into this just for kicks.","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016},{"text":"Just fire up that machine over there, and you’ll be... transformed. No one will be able to touch you, much less take you down.","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016},{"text":"I'll take it upstairs. Once you get stronger, you'll move up the ladder too. Say goodbye to grunt work.","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016},{"text":"HAHAHA! We did it! Such a genius move, using human frequencies to take down Tacet Discord’s!","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016},{"text":"As long as Tacet Discords understand our language, we can boss them around however we want!","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016},{"text":"Shut down the Photonvault and release our new friend… I mean, old friend! Even that Rover won't stand a chance!","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016},{"text":"Ogo? Can you hear me? How’s your new body feeling? I get it, four legs might be a challenge at first. Take your time.","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016},{"text":"What? Don’t be stupid. We combined his with the Tacet Discord’s frequencies. Of course you can’t see his, moron!","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016},{"text":"This isn’t funny! Ogo, wake up! Now isn’t the time for a nap… No, no… Stay back! STAY BACK!","quest_name":"Lores Beyond the Ranges","quest_id":11900016}]}